latestPosts.caption:
Low porosity hair. Oily scalp. Frizzy, dry ends.

Yup, that’s the trio I’ve been *battling* — until I cracked the code 💁🏻‍♀️✨

💧 **L’Oréal shampoo** when it’s just greasy – cleanses deep with salicylic acid & hydrates with hyaluronic acid
🌿 **Tea Tree shampoo** when it’s greasy *and* itchy – instantly soothes and refreshes
🧴 **Hydrating conditioner** just on the ends – no oily scalp, just soft strands
🧖‍♀️ **Microfiber towel** – frizz = minimized, breakage = reduced
💫 **Lightweight serum** on the ends – seals in shine and smoothness

This 5-step routine makes my hair feel balanced, clean, and cute every time 🧼✨

👇
**Drop a 💆‍♀️ if this sounds like your hair struggle too**
📌 Save this reel for your next wash day
💌 Send it to your BFF who’s *always* complaining about oily scalp + dry ends 😅
